title: KDFX DriverPack + SabLab v1.0 (2011) [Multilenguaje]
description:
KDFX DriverPack + SabLab v1.0 (2011) [Multilenguaje]

--------
English:
--------
Category: Utilities TEU 
Language: Multilingual including Spanish 
Operating System: Windows XP/Vista/7 

Description: 
------------ 
Collection of drivers and SamLab KDFX for all Windows 32-bit and 64 bit Windows 2000 to Windows 7, including server platforms (Vista x32/64 eliminated). As the shell-installer program used Assistant Drivers Installation and Troubleshooting DriverPack 11 Pro to automatically detect your hardware and automatically install the necessary drivers! The collection includes the latest at the time of collecting personal SamLab KDFX driver and video additions NVIDIA, ATI Radeon chipset. Do not confuse this package with the driver packages Bashrat and others - the current driver is newer and more stable than others, because SamLab is a member of the team Bashrat and has the ability to know about all the problems of a controller similar to the packages create their own set of the most complete and at peace! 

Orignal provider download -> Freshwap.com 

In compiling the package used: 

-Shell to install the drivers DriverPack solution BadPointer 
-Shell to install the drivers for the driver installation wizard Romeo91 
-Shell to backup drivers backup solutions Romeo91 drivers 
Driver packs SamDrivers collection created with DriverPacks Team
